The Stormers are still adapting to life on the road. Competing in the United Rugby Championship as well as the Champions Cup has taken some getting used to. Spirits are high in the camp ahead of their next match. eNCA’s Justin Ford reports. #dstv403 CAPE TOWN - The Stormers next face Clermont Auvergne in the Champions Cup. The Cape side needs just a point to advance to the playoff stages of the competition. Coach John Dobson wants his team to dominate their French opponents and earn a home playoff berth. * eNCA’s Justin Ford reports.